overview: Alice Cooper at Cidade do Rock, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil on September 21, 2017. Setlist: Brutal Planet / No More Mr. Nice Guy / Under My Wheels / Guitar Solo (Nita Strauss) / Poison / Halo of Flies (with drum solo) / Feed My Frankenstein / Cold Ethyl / Only Women Bleed / Killer / I Love the Dead (band vocals only) / Fire / School's Out
title: Alice Cooper: Rock In Rio 2017
